window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>What if decemancy isn't enough?</b></p><p>Powerful forces threaten the stability of both the West and the entire world. The Eldemari's ambition, a descendant vanquisher: everyone is out for Ian's head. The odds are long, even with Euryphel's Regret and End affinities shifting the rhythm of war.</p><p>Ian must plumb the depths of a new area of magic, one he swore off years ago: the forbidden study of the soul—necromancy.</p><p>But first, he needs to find a teacher.</p>"; 
